 <path class="yelp-svg-fill" d="m17 16h4l-5 5v-4c0-0.554 0.446-1 1-1z"></path>
</svg><div class="inner"><div class="region"><div class="contents"><p class="p">In the <span class="gui">Activities</span> overview, you are always able to long-press
    to right-click, even with this feature disabled. Long-press works slightly
    differently in the overview: you do not have to release the button to
    right-click.</p></div></div></div>
</div>
